    categorySlug: '/category/wholesale-and-distribution/',
    excerpt: 'As the Federal Board of Revenue (FBR) continues to strengthen Pakistan\'s tax system, digital invoicing has become a critical requirement for businesses. Both retailers and wholesalers are required to generate FBR-compliant invoices...',
